name: ✴ 𝕲𝖍𝖔𝖘𝖙 ✴
description:
✴ Portrait of Ghost

Ghost cover itself in fear of the others. It needs more courage, even when it is full of stars underneath the sheet itself. If it knows, it would uncover itself someday.

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consisting of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
